<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>118</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lí kāi gù xiāng de xiǎo hé, lí kāi mén qián de bái yáng,
 jiǎo bù tà shàng yì tǔ tā xiāng.
 fēng yǔ jiān chéng de rì zi lǐ, gù xiāng de qīn rén zuì nán wàng,
 yuàn shén bǎo shǒu nǐ men xīn líng ān kāng.
 nǐ men zài shān de nà yī biān, wǒ zài shuǐ de zhè yī fāng,
 shén zhù fú nǐ de gù xiāng, yě shì wǒ de gù xiāng,
 rú yé hé huá de yuán zi, huá měi xìng wàng,
 shēng mìng de quán shuǐ liú bù xī, yǒng xiàng sì fāng, yǒng xiàng sì fāng.</lyrics>
<title>sī niàn gù xiāng 迦南118</title>
</song>